esta pelicula no fue un buen proyecto,casi me duermo en el trascurso de ella y hasta la adelante en muchas escenas,me  gustan las peliculas que presentan la tematica de cuba,pero esta cinta es facil de olvidar!

From across the gulf comes this nice surprise.  Well acted and directed, Personal Belongings tells the story of a lady who does not desire to leave her homeland, and the young man she meets who desires to leave Cuba anyway he can.  With rich characters and scenery of urban/suburban life, we get a good depiction of life in Cuba.  My only reservation about this film is that the ending wraps up suddenly and is a bit cheesy.
